name: Package Stores, Beer, Wine, and Liquor

description:
Merchants that sell packaged alcoholic beverages such as ale, beer,
wine, and liquor for consumption off the premises. Such merchants
may or may not also sell a limited variety of snack items,
newspapers, and magazines, or toiletries and over-the-counter
medicines.
For merchants that sell liquor for consumption on the premises, use
MCC 5813.
